  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of EVERA to Augment Small Breast</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized-Controlled Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Breast Augmentation With EVERA(Korean External Soft Tissue Expansion System) as Compared to AESTES (American External Soft Tissue Expansion</official_title>
  <sponsors>
